<FlowDocument PagePadding="5,0,5,0" AllowDrop="True" NumberSubstitution.CultureSource="User" xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"><Paragraph><Run FontFamily="Verdana" FontWeight="Bold" FontSize="13.3333333333333" xml:lang="en-ca">Shrink Image Size</Run></Paragraph><Paragraph><Run FontFamily="Calibri" FontSize="13.3333333333333" xml:lang="en-ca">Here you can specify the expected new size of output images as long as the mode how to calculate new image size. There 3 modes you can choose:</Run></Paragraph><List MarkerStyle="Disc"><ListItem><Paragraph><Run FontFamily="Verdana" FontWeight="Bold" FontSize="13.3333333333333" xml:lang="en-ca">By Long Side</Run><Run FontFamily="Calibri" FontSize="13.3333333333333" xml:lang="en-ca" xml:space="preserve"> - application will take the new size entered by you and make it as the new image size of long side. For example if you have an image with resolution of 800 * 600 (wider image) and you input 400 as new size, the output image will have 400 * 300 as new resolution; if you have an image with resolution of 600 * 800 (taller image) and you input 400 as new size, the output image will have 300 * 400 as new resolution. The aspect ratio will be persisted in new image.</Run></Paragraph></ListItem><ListItem><Paragraph><Run FontFamily="Verdana" FontWeight="Bold" FontSize="13.3333333333333" xml:lang="en-ca">By Width</Run><Run FontFamily="Calibri" FontSize="13.3333333333333" xml:lang="en-ca" xml:space="preserve"> - application will take the new size entered by you and make it as new image width. The aspect ratio will be persisted in new image.</Run></Paragraph></ListItem><ListItem><Paragraph><Run FontFamily="Verdana" FontWeight="Bold" FontSize="13.3333333333333" xml:lang="en-ca">By Height</Run><Run FontFamily="Calibri" FontSize="13.3333333333333" xml:lang="en-ca" xml:space="preserve"> - application will take the new size entered by you and make it as new image height. The aspect ratio will be persisted in new image.</Run></Paragraph></ListItem></List><Paragraph><Run FontFamily="Calibri" FontWeight="Bold" FontSize="13.3333333333333" xml:lang="en-ca">Note</Run><Run FontFamily="Calibri" FontSize="13.3333333333333" xml:lang="en-ca" xml:space="preserve">: </Run></Paragraph><List MarkerStyle="Disc"><ListItem><Paragraph><Run FontFamily="Calibri" FontSize="13.3333333333333" xml:lang="en-ca">If the entered new size of image in any of the choice above results image enlargement, the application will keep original image resolution.</Run></Paragraph></ListItem><ListItem><Paragraph><Run FontFamily="Calibri" FontSize="13.3333333333333" xml:lang="en-ca">If the entered new size of image is 0, the application will keep original image resolution.</Run></Paragraph></ListItem></List></FlowDocument>